              "correct": false,
              "hint": "But the gate is right here! Tell him to stop near it: 'gate hattira nilisi'."
            },
            {
              "kannada": "Gate beda, hogtaa irona.",
              "script": "ಗೇಟ್ ಬೇಡ, ಹೋಗ್ತಾ ಇರೋಣ.",
              "pronunciation": "gate BEH-da, HOG-taa i-RO-na",
              "english": "No gate, let's keep going.",
