          "kannada": "Ido togoli, chillare ide. Dhanyavada saar!",
          "script": "ಇದೋ ತೊಗೊಳಿ, ಚಿಲ್ಲರೆ ಇದೆ. ಧನ್ಯವಾದ ಸಾರ್!",
          "pronunciation": "i-do to-GO-li, CHIL-la-re i-de. DHAN-ya-vaa-da saar",
          "english": "Here, take it, I have exact change. Thank you sir!"
        }
      ]
    }
